            <![CDATA[
                    <p><img src="https://www.fassbender.studio/media/posts/7/clay-banks-Hnec2oEbbxk-unsplash.jpg" class="type:primaryImage" alt="" /></p>
                <p style="font-size: 0.667rem; line-height: 1rem; text-align: start;" data-font-size-lg="0.667rem" data-line-height-lg="1.000rem" data-font-size-md="0.667rem" data-line-height-md="1.000rem" data-font-size-sm="0.667rem" data-line-height-sm="1.000rem" data-font-size-xs="0.667rem" data-line-height-xs="1.000rem" data-font-size-xl="0.833rem" data-line-height-xl="1.222rem" data-text-align-xl="start">Lunatti is a fashion brand characterised by a design approach that marries contemporary trends with timeless elegance.</p>
<p style="font-size: 0.667rem; line-height: 1rem; text-align: start;" data-font-size-lg="0.667rem" data-line-height-lg="1.000rem" data-font-size-md="0.667rem" data-line-height-md="1.000rem" data-font-size-sm="0.667rem" data-line-height-sm="1.000rem" data-font-size-xs="0.667rem" data-line-height-xs="1.000rem" data-font-size-xl="0.833rem" data-line-height-xl="1.222rem" data-text-align-xl="start">The project brief called for understated distinction to create a sense of trust while giving prominence to the garments.</p>
<p style="font-size: 0.667rem; line-height: 1rem; text-align: start;" data-font-size-lg="0.667rem" data-line-height-lg="1.000rem" data-font-size-md="0.667rem" data-line-height-md="1.000rem" data-font-size-sm="0.667rem" data-line-height-sm="1.000rem" data-font-size-xs="0.667rem" data-line-height-xs="1.000rem" data-font-size-xl="0.833rem" data-line-height-xl="1.222rem" data-text-align-xl="start">kkkkTwo wordmarks—primary and secondary—were designed for use. The contrasting line weights and bespoke letterforms in the primary option create a contemporary feel, while the secondary, cursive design is crafted from handwriting samples supplied by the client, giving added ownership and personality. Both wordmarks are supplemented with a brand symbol that’s ideal for use in small spaces, and all elements are displayed in a muted, minimal palette for a high-end impression.</p>
